Package: zerotier-gui
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pyqt6 (>= 6.4), python3-pyqt6.qtsvg, policykit-1
Maintainer: Alessandro <alessandro@zerotier-gui>
Description: ZeroTier Network Manager - GUI
 A graphical interface for managing ZeroTier networks.
 Provides a system tray icon, network join/leave, peer list,
 and service start/stop via Polkit authentication.
Homepage: https://github.com/alessandro/zerotier-gui
